articles.title: Mort Sahl, satirist who revolutionized stand-up comedy, dead at 94 - cbc.ca
articles.description: Satirist Mort Sahl, whose running commentary on politicians and current events during the Cold War made him a favourite of a new, restive generation of Americans, died Tuesday. He was 94.
